categories: Category:Grand Army of the Republic battalions

nodes.text: The 05 Commando battalion, or Zero Five Commando was one of the ten Commando Groups subordinated under the Special Operations Brigade. The unit was a battalion of clone commandos, led by Jedi General Bardan Jusik. Omega, Delta, and Veshok squads were part of the unit.
Following Jusik's resignation, Etain Tur-Mukan assumed command of the unit.
